Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! You'll lose your arm!\NIts sharpness is the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find Luffy! He's gotta be hiding\Nsomewhere in Loguetown still!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will show himself to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The execution platform!\NThe execution platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the view the King\Nof the Pirates saw before he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... which way is\Nthe execution platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Usopp vs. Daddy the Parent;\NShowdown at High Noon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this man named Luffy\Nreally still on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry and blockade the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so easygoing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop!\N--Hey! You can't come in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the navy captain's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Heya, Smoker.\N--So it's you, Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Two-Pistol Pete and\Nthe Police-Killer Riley Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three have bounties, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also dropped one off at the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need your signature\Nand I can get my money today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One million Berries for four people?\NThese are all small fries...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted men headed for the\NGrand Line gather in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can earn money\Nmore efficiently this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than looking high\Nand low for just one big name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Navy's most gifted snipers,\Nreduced to bullying weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you've fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't feel like putting\Nmy life in my guns' hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if you die, your\Ndaughter'll wind up on the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Carol my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll tell her the\Nold smoky man said hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Daddy Masterson,\Nthe bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We joined at\Nthe same time, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was an elite, on the fast track\Nto being a key player at Navy HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is he doing this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cursed sword, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's a cool sword you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, what're you doing here?\N--Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you acting cocky about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, tell me.\N--Hey! There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How do I get to the execution platform?\N--It's him! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that?\N--You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you sell our\Nbuddies to the Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna pay big-time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run on home and have your\Nmama bake you a cake, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old guy's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that man might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Daddy the Parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought a lot! A real lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my preparations to be a brave\Nwarrior of the sea are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I'm forgetting now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I forgot\Nthe most important thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goggles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A top-class sniper needs\Nto have top-class goggles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just basic! The most basic of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Investing every last bit of money\Nto get the best goggles around
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the spirit of a top-class sniper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goggles! Goggles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These ones! These goggles!\NIt's gotta be these! I like 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a good eye! Them's the\Nlatest North Blue model there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got 'em from an import ship that\Nleaves the Navy only once a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You got no money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't do business with\Npeople who don't got money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it gonna be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Right! Backpack, backpack...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take these goggles, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My! What a cute little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes! You're in luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only pair\Nof these goggles in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the first to--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butt out... old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop right there, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Let's set the record\Nstraight! I am not an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Mister"! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What for?! You're an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, you said it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme those goggles back!\NI found 'em first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up yer damn complainin'\Nand I'll call the marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marines?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I'm friends with\Na navy captain in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old smoky man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't know who I am, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Great Captain Usopp! I destroyed\NArlong's fishman pirate group!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was truly a battle to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, surrounded by 200--\Nno, 300 fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All alone, I punched, threw, stomped,\Nkicked, and tore them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I now have a\N30 million Berry bounty on my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. 30 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Papa!\N--Papa?! Why am I your papa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a present for you, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Carol...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice, angelic girl you are!\NI love you, Carol-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! I love you, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with this family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But guess what! That old man there\Nis trying to swipe your present!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now! You mustn't say "swipe"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good manners, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who's\Nbullying my adorable Carol?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Bullying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's not all!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a bounty of\N30 million Berries, I hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the new wanted posters?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got 'em from\Nthe outpost just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,600,000... 1,300,000... 700,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million... Straw Hat Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A starting bounty at this amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obviously not the person\Non that poster! I was just lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My funny plan to trick people was\Na great success! Ha ha! Well, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-That's right!\NIt sure is! That's me, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you this!\NJust you try and lay a hand on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My captain Luffy won't sit by quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an evil,\Ncold-blooded, devilish man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever defied him\Nand lived to tell about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a kid, right?\NYou should really value your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That sounds bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, given that this Luffy\Nfellow is worth 30 million Berries,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's clearly no ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! You're obviously\Nway stronger, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the strongest guy in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carol. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is that I make\Nenough money to live happily with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far more important to me\Nthan being the world's greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy's wimping out\Nafter I said all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! In that case...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?! Now do you see\Nhow terrifying I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my advice! Just hand\Nthose goggles over to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'll pay for 'em!\NSo just give 'em here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you saying that right after\Nhe's just about to let you go--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Papa?\N--Then let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you have no problem\Nwith us settling this in a fair fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fight?\N--Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight? Y-You're not\Ntalking about a duel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, the goggles are yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6... 30 pistols?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Daddy the Parent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The very same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A showdown!\N--There's gonna be a showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy the Parent's\Ngonna duel somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say Daddy the Parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy the Parent is the\Ngreatest gunslinger bounty hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the East Blue knows that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the idiot who'd\Nchallenge him to a duel looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Long-nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry if he beats ya!\NWe already got a place dug for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did things turn out\Nthis way? Am I an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple. We both\Nwalk 10 paces and then shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Y-Yeah...\N--What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Daddy the Parent\Nin a duel... Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shut up! Things just turned\Nout this way! Shut up and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get one shot. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... Really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can possibly\Nbeat Daddy the Parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to die here?!\NThis can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just started my adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even gained any courage\Nor manliness or anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! You're amazing, Papa!\NYou're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Man, how pathetic.\N--What a lame duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd have more guts\Nthan that. What a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only shot his gun away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!\NTryin' to cheat like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward! Weakling!\NCan't you even fight honestly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! Forgive me!\NI'm just a lowly, pathetic man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking the life of someone like\Nme wouldn't gain you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you just peacefully let me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--W-Wait!\N--Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! If it's money you\Nwant, she has tons of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please don't shoot me!\NPlease spare my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you're trying\Nto hide behind a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Forget what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just an innocent bystander\Nwho has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wind up getting shot,\NI can't let her get caught up in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Usopp...\N--Please! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Usopp..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your name Usopp, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know a man named\NYasopp of the Red-Haired Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasopp? That's my old man's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've met my dad before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you are his son...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never once told a soul\Nwhat happened on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened at a hot, dry\Nport town, much like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:15:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Ensign Masterson!\NWe each get one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He won!\N--Yasopp won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out! He beat one\Nof the Navy's best snipers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was truly a close fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man, Yasopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasopp! Finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Killin' the loser of\Na duel is a sign of kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me! Now that I've lost a duel,\NI have no reason to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You've got good resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A navy ensign of all people,\Ncarefully treasuring something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be really spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lecture me, you filthy pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were great, Yasopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain of this wound just goes\Nto show how inexperienced I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took on Daddy Masterson!\NYou won because you're you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never would've stood a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your watching\Nthe duel without saying anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the stuff!\NYou want some, Ensign?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family's not so bad.\NBut I'm no good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a son of my own.\NHis name's Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen him in years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit the high seas around\Nthe time he was a toddler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Do you not love your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Jolly Roger was calling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell 'im, Yasopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one hopeless\Nparent like me is too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always stay by your daughter's side.\NYou can't let her feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm in no position to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost our duel!\NYasopp! Finish me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me your lousy sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You navy guys might hang us by\Nour necks right after you catch us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we pirates are free to let you\Nlive or die however we please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why a navy elite\Nturned to bounty-hunting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! You lost to a pirate,\NPapa?! He spared your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it isn't true, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's amazing!\NYour dad must be really skilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even beat Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus he hadn't forgotten about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now,\Nwhen he's living an adventure,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he has an image of you\Netched in his memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I can understand\Nhow you'd feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not why...\NThat's not why I'm crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you normally do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you normally tell\Nsome pathetic boy like me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a story about you shamelessly\Nhaving your life spared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that to give me courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people would be vain\Nand keep a story like that secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me even though you\Nknew it'd make you less cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how brave my\Nold man might be! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weaklings or cowards\Ncould never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carol! Your dad is\Nthe bravest man alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find strong guys any old place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never seen a man as\Nstrong and kind as your dad before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't give in, either! I gotta\Nbe brave, or I'll shame your dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy! Give me a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me in another life-or-death match!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cheat anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. This will be our real match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose the weapon\Nyou're most skilled with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Now, then. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and hit that weathervane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weathervane? That?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! You can shoot\Nme right through the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life is on the line for real this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can\Nshoot that far with that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just like always...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shoot like you always do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Papa! Don't shoot him! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shoot him. Usopp shot\Nright through its crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He really did!\NRight through the crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an excellent shot.\NI'd expect no less of Yasopp's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forget that bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday you will\Nbecome like your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the Grand Line.\NI'm certain Yasopp is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Papa!\N--Carol, you know that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's poor manners to say, "So long!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm sorry, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to grow up to be a nice\Nlady worthy of being your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already plenty\Nnice as you are now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm going to be an even nicer lady!\N--Even when people say he's a\Ndisgrace behind his back now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's fought all this time\Nto protect the one he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a\Nbrave man like Daddy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become a real warrior\Nand stand before my dad someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! I've been looking for you, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying there's\Na cooking contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.71,0:24:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Cooking techniques aren't\Nmeant for competing against people!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're for delighting Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're not gonna enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.22,0:24:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get that if you win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.85,0:24:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's... an elephant bluefin tuna!
